 \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Last Supper visually represents the last time that Jesus broke bread with his twelve disciples before he was arrested and hung on a cross.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1501, \"end\": 1506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.999994555899815, \"rank\": 5.444125756342357e-06, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the Last Supper also marks the first-ever sacrament of Holy Communion, in which Christians are united with Jesus Christ (Yeshua), receiving his grace and forgiveness.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1659, \"end\": 1673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"score\": 0.9999799189465114, \"rank\": 2.0081321350410213e-05, \"text\": \"Holy Communion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\"}, {\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.8742763401218125, \"rank\": 0.1398101710341261, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999962842969946, \"rank\": 3.715716690431759e-06, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 1725, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.862108009286206e-21, \"text\": \"Yeshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088